data.description:
Welcome to your dream home in the coveted Rainbow Lakes community of Boynton Beach! This charming single-story residence offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience.Boasting 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home features a thoughtfully designed split bedroom layout, providing both privacy and functionality. The master bedroom is a retreat in itself, complete with an ensuite bath and a spacious walk-in closet.As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the inviting ambiance of a vaulted ceiling, creating an open and airy feel throughout the living spaces. The family room is conveniently adjacent to the breakfast area, making it the ideal spot to gather and relax. With the laundry conveniently located inside, your daily chores become a breeze. But what truly sets this home apart is its waterfront location, offering serene views and a sense of tranquility. Enjoy the beauty of the outdoors from the screened patio, a perfect place for relaxation and entertainment.

You'll appreciate the practicality of an attached 2-car garage, providing ample storage space and shelter for your vehicles.

Location is key, and this home is perfectly situated just minutes away from the Turnpike, I-95, Wellington, Boynton Beach, Downtown West Palm Beach, and the stunning area beaches. Additionally, you'll have easy access to three international airports, ensuring you're well-connected to the world.

Rainbow Lakes is a well-maintained community that offers its residents an array of resort-style amenities, enhancing your quality of life. Don't miss your chance to own this fantastic home in a prime location. Your slice of paradise awaits!
